{"tid":2015814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】日奧運選手良心有愧拒收贊助 改送外賣賺錢兼保持體能","createTime":"2020-05-14T03:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T17:54:04.000Z","uid":242396,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b47ad6486261f49a18788978812101c936eb40ec","tid":2015814,"uid":242396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"日本東京奧運因疫情而延期，主要靠贊助維持收入的運動員生計也受影響。曾奪奧運劍擊團體項目銀牌的三宅諒（Ryo Miyake）轉行送外賣，他指送外賣可「避免我的體能變弱」，既可鍛鍊又能賺錢，是渡過這段抗疫時間的不錯選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/n4PUjlDw3LUUEdepyo3MY62dgb4=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3U52BKIZKI2I35AHSPIIOU2O7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fn4PUjlDw3LUUEdepyo3MY62dgb4%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3U52BKIZKI2I35AHSPIIOU2O7Q.jpg&h=757ab106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三宅諒曾代表日本參加2012年倫敦奧運的男子個人花劍及男子團體花劍，於團體賽獲得銀牌。因疫情關係所有劍擊比賽要取消，暫時未知奧運運動員資格的安排，他表示︰「在這種狀態接受贊助我覺得良心有愧，所以我要求他們暫時停止資助。」<br />\n<br />\n收入中斷之外，健身室也因防疫要關閉，三宅諒需要找新方法賺錢和保持體能。他認為為外賣公司工作，既有助鍛鍊亦可賺錢，而且工時彈性、容易適應，「送外賣有助防止我的體能變弱」。<br />\n<br />\n三宅諒平均每天只賺到2000日圓（約144港元），但他本身有積蓄，可以維持生活。在防疫居家令實施期間，外賣服務需求上升，加上公司提供「零接觸」送餐服務，顧客可選擇餐飲只放在門前，三宅諒也不擔心因送貨而受感染，「染疫的風險很低，雖然你可能覺得送貨需要與很多人接觸，但就如程式建議，我會將食物放在客人家門前，沒有接觸。唯一的接觸是我在餐廳，從職員手上取餐」。<br />\n<br />\n奧運延期，三宅諒未取得代表出賽資格，他也未知會否獲選拔去接受訓練，「劍擊是一種不適合目前情況的運動，因為我們一定要相聚才能練習，很遺憾，我希望重新開始，見到所有人能沒有顧慮自由練習」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/1Y_Xu5uwc1cHlh0Ylnt3l8wT9rQ=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QDPNGWNMDXL5EYUMBUGISH4KJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F1Y_Xu5uwc1cHlh0Ylnt3l8wT9rQ%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQDPNGWNMDXL5EYUMBUGISH4KJQ.jpg&h=6ab9bc67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路透社/《蘋果》資料室<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200513/DUJVUKDESHKL4QDINJETVF3PXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200513%2FDUJVUKDESHKL4QDINJETVF3PXE%2F&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=63ea2059\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200513%2FDUJVUKDESHKL4QDINJETVF3PXE%2F&h=eac78b18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200513/DUJVUKDESHKL4QDINJETVF3PXE/</a>"},{"pid":"5cf6efb971b45a2303513a10a1eda8ab9cffe86b","tid":2015814,"uid":242396,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"他指送外賣可「避免我的體能變弱」，既可鍛鍊又能賺錢，是渡過這段抗疫時間的不錯選擇<br />\n<br />\n咪笑外賣仔了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eafb27407511f324addf2e0c51b345cef37cb0d","tid":2015814,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"留名等睇破壞之王2"},{"pid":"9dd00ca98a1d6dac8c0435f890e06c9ac5c9b36f","tid":2015814,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"我係話在座咁多位"},{"pid":"0afe640159792c258d594a13e1623f18685b7a9a","tid":2015814,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"加底幾錢呀"},{"pid":"707bb7c18568be726ce7542a3f3bc103fc4087e6","tid":2015814,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"冇人既?"},{"pid":"254ee4a7fdafe79d4d17ff6023c8a3edce58b6bb","tid":2015814,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7eafb27407511f324addf2e0c51b345cef37cb0d","tid":2015814,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"留名等睇破壞之王2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"日本古劍法"},{"pid":"e8d6281588c179dbd56d